title: New York explorers find 1862 shipwreck in Lake Ontario
text:
Published By: Reuters - US News - Today 
NEW YORK (Reuters) - A team of shipwreck explorers has discovered a mid-19th century sunken steamship, believed to be the oldest of its kind...
